                        <p class="para-desc text-muted" style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; opacity: 0; animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards; animation-delay: 0.3s;">
                            A cybersecurity leader with over a decade of experience in threat intelligence, incident response, and security assessments. Passionate about OSINT, building security automation, and mentoring the next generation of cybersecurity professionals.
                        </p>
                        <div class="mt-4 pt-2" style="opacity: 0; animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards; animation-delay: 0.4s;">
