                        <h5 class="exp-title">Senior Security Operations Engineer</h5>
                        <p class="exp-company">Microsoft</p>
                        <p class="exp-description">
                            Part of Microsoft's Cyber Defense Operations Center, where I focus on rapid threat response and containment across global enterprise environments. My day-to-day involves building automation to minimize impact and keep operations running smoothly.
                        </p>
