                        <p class="exp-company">Zemoso Technologies</p>
                        <p class="exp-description">
                            As the sole security lead reporting to the CTO, I owned everything security — from cloud posture across GCP, AWS, and Azure to deploying Wazuh SIEM and building SOAR workflows that cut our response times significantly.
