                        <p class="exp-company">Prime Healthcare</p>
                        <p class="exp-description">
                            Led the Cyber Threat Intelligence function for a network of hospitals. Built automation scripts that streamlined our CTI workflows, authored TTP reports, and helped secure IoT medical devices across the healthcare group.
                        </p>
