                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Deloitte USI -->
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6">
                    <div class="experience-card">
                        <span class="exp-duration">May 2017 – October 2018</span>
                        <h5 class="exp-title">Senior Analyst – Cyber Threat Intelligence</h5>
